</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-96_"><strong>Production Practices: </strong>These brands adopt ethical, eco-conscious production methods that reduce water and energy consumption, minimize waste, and ensure fair working conditions.




</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-98_"><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong>Social awareness and environmental education: </strong>They actively educate consumers about the environmental and social impacts of fashion, empowering them to make informed purchasing decisions [12,13].




