</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-110_"><strong>Empowered Consumers: </strong>These initiatives empower consumers to become conscious buyers, making informed choices about the clothes they purchase and the brands they support.





</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-112_"><strong>Shift in Values: </strong>They promote a shift in consumer values, encouraging people to prioritize quality over quantity, durability over disposability, and ethical production over fast fashion trends.





